  "description": "A singularity is a point or region where [general relativity](../../../terms/general-relativity.md) predicts infinite spacetime curvature and infinite density. It appears at the center of a [black hole](./black-hole.md) and at the origin of the [Big Bang](../../evolution/terms/big-bang.md).",
